off-line using processing steps to remove distortions caused by magnetic
ﬁeld inhomogeneity and other sources of misalignment to the structural
data, which yields excellent coverage of subcortical areas of interest.
2.5. Imaging data analysis
2.5.1. MRI Pre-processing
Anatomical images were homogeneity-corrected using SPM2, then
skull-stripped using the Brain Extraction Tool in FSL (version 5.0.7)
